"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"12月12日消息，《富爸爸穷爸爸》作者罗伯特·清崎（Robert Kiyosaki）表示，市场崩盘和大萧条即将到来，他预测“黄金、白银、[比特币](https://www.bitcoin86.com/)和房地产也将崩盘。”他补充说，他准备在市场崩盘后买入所有这四类投资。\",\"timestamp\":1639313790,\"title\":\"《富爸爸穷爸爸》作者：预测黄金、白银、比特币和房地产即将崩盘，并准备抄底\"},\"digest\":\"aSWkdlTAWEFJVMxmlbcAGdKXTAXjDxXqLKbICckIu5k\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x0457aE7187F8A64DeF7De84E8D9212C108605CA5\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"fsmDWCLqm8xtP6MbiPFZMbBt94FlPciDyYLR3zoK-e0\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"zECP7qaDYK-NdILgNljMuStfzhaqBLY0cOEuIrIDhwE\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"3KNmEWu7og-8yX94woM-dlqec9pSyix8HkA4VfGQN0Br34fBduvIx3ZBjBoCl1B0-K87TvgWaQPzapkdXvc-Uw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x489fd4c68260d535ec4e9994c5d70282596766fc6593371afb101dfa386a6fd0457b9ed3522b4c8527ae429ed01a236747b36902980e4f659663bd4f1a1a86171c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"fsmDWCLqm8xtP6MbiPFZMbBt94FlPciDyYLR3zoK-e0\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"zECP7qaDYK-NdILgNljMuStfzhaqBLY0cOEuIrIDhwE\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"aSWkdlTAWEFJVMxmlbcAGdKXTAXjDxXqLKbICckIu5k\"}"